Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.69,0:23:51.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石橋下尉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.22,0:23:56.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用女子劍道征服世界的作戰  運作正常嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.79,0:23:57.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  很不好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.14,0:23:59.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.20,0:24:02.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回已經是第15話了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.19,0:24:05.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要首次合宿和首次上澡堂了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.53,0:24:07.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在搞什麼鬼！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.35,0:24:08.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對…對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.04,0:24:11.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不趕快完成作戰的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.38,0:24:13.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙…那傢伙就要來了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.23,0:24:17.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,D…Death Armor大人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.36,0:24:19.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你這傢伙！
